## 🩺 Overview
This project is a professional digital ecosystem designed to showcase the intersection of 20+ years of clinical leadership and modern cloud engineering. As the HOD of Emergency Medicine at Madadeni Regional Hospital, I developed these tools to solve real-world operational gaps in healthcare using the Salesforce platform and front-end web technologies.

## 🚀 Featured Projects
* **Emergency Department Assistant:** A diagnostic support tool built to assist junior doctors in high-pressure trauma settings.
* **Madadeni Roster System:** A digitized operational tool designed to streamline district-wide clinical staffing.
* **Salesforce Lead Engine:** A conceptual build demonstrating Web-to-Lead automation and SDR coordination.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
* **Core:** HTML5, CSS3 (Modern Glassmorphism), JavaScript (ES6+)
* **Ecosystem:** Salesforce Lightning Experience, Flow Builder, Salesforce CRM logic
* **Tools:** Git, GitHub, CLI, VS Code, Netlify

## 📈 Impact
The educational components within this portfolio (A&E Learning Group) currently support a cohort of over **400 doctors and students** globally, providing streamlined access to clinical protocols and peer-to-peer mentorship.

